documents.title: New Ventures - Operational Overhead Calculation
documents.content:
New Ventures Operational Overhead calculation



"How it works

This sheet provides the percentage of operational overhead (i.e. KTLO work per month). Each team has a dedicated tab. For this to work, you need to
* add the label KTLO to all Jira tickets that you consider KTLO work
* Make sure all tickets that move into the “resolved” state have assigned story points. Add the actual story point in hindsight for accurate operational overhead calculation
A cron job runs every night and updates this sheet. It used the resolved date to include a ticket in the calculation for a specific month.
"

They were not aware that they had to order from Factor to get ready-to-eat low-carb meals. They had to throw away the two meals they received from HelloFresh and were charged for them. The customer said they would never order from HelloFresh again and had already filed a dispute. The agent informed the customer that HelloFresh is a self-managing account, and the customer needs to check the menus and make changes themselves. The agent offered to file a report for the issue with the box the customer received, but the customer ended the conversation.",Other Customer Care of System Error,Payment Processing Issues,Complaint - Quality,2025-10-26T19:15:58.841Z,2025-10-26T19:39:05.096Z,2025-W44,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,US

The agent confirmed the order and informed the customer that the order was cancelled and a refund would be issued. The agent also confirmed that the customer's HelloFresh account was still active and the next delivery was scheduled for November 2. The customer asked if there was a way to try a free Factor box, but the agent informed them that there was no promotion for a free box.",NON Cancellation,Managing Order Cancellations,Account - 1st Box Change / Question,2025-10-26T22:05:43.583Z,2025-10-26T22:22:04.781Z,2025-W44,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,US

10/26/2025,65253551,6c564f3a-449e-4d73-9d3a-0ff650063dec,Voice,"discuss their order and account settings. They had recently changed their order to include Factor meals instead of Hello Fresh meals, but were unsure how to cancel their Hello Fresh subscription. The agent clarified that canceling the Hello Fresh subscription would also prevent the customer from ordering Factor meals. The customer wanted to change their Hello Fresh meal plan size to 2 meals for 2 people instead of the original 3 meals for 2 people. The agent successfully made this change and informed the customer that they could skip future Hello Fresh deliveries up to 5 days before the delivery date. The customer also wanted to know if they could still order Factor meals if they canceled their Hello Fresh subscription, and the agent confirmed that they could order Factor meals through their own website. The customer expressed that they may try Hello Fresh again in the future and thanked the agent for their help.",Meal Selection/Menu/Recipes,Meal Selection Customization Issues,Account - Update account / subscription details,2025-10-26T22:19:50.488Z,2025-10-26T22

They requested a refund and wanted to ensure that it would not happen again. The agent verified the customer's account information and promised to look into the issue. The customer was asked to provide their full name and email address for verification purposes. The agent also asked if the delivery date in question was for that day, but the customer did not respond. The chat ended due to inactivity, and the agent advised the customer to start a new message if they needed further assistance.",Other Customer Care of System Error,Unauthorized account charge issues,Account - After deadline change request,2025-11-23T14:11:02.980Z,2025-11-23T14:24:30.448Z,2025-W48,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,US

They were informed that they had accepted a cross-selling offer for the Factor meals and that the order could not be cancelled as it was past the cut-off period. The customer insisted on cancelling their entire account and the Factor subscription that was initiated in error. The agent confirmed that the account was cancelled and advised the customer to contact [name] for further assistance.,Account Cancellation,Customer Inquiries and Requests,Payments - Credit/ Refund,2025-11-23T14:24:24.289Z,2025-11-23T14:47:29.350Z,2025-W48,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,US

The customer then mentioned that they had received a discount and that the order total was different from what they expected. The agent asked for a screenshot to investigate the issue and confirmed that it was a glitch on the website. The agent informed the customer that they would still receive the box, but it would be free. The agent checked if there were any other issues and then ended the chat due to inactivity.",Box Cancellation,Unspecified Purchase Reasons,Other - Connection Issue,2025-11-24T16:50:47.486Z,2025-11-24T17:07:43.546Z,2025-W48,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,null,US
